Package: shutdowntimer
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: FakyLab <https://github.com/FakyLab>
Homepage: https://github.com/FakyLab/ShutdownTimer
Depends: libqt6widgets6 (>= 6.5), libqt6gui6 (>= 6.5), libqt6core6 (>= 6.5), qt6-qpa-plugins, libglib2.0-0, libpolkit-gobject-1-0, libc6 (>= 2.17)
Recommends: policykit-1
Description: Cross-platform shutdown and restart timer
 Shutdown Timer lets you schedule system shutdowns, restarts,
 hibernation, and sleep after a countdown or at a specific time.
 It also lets you set a custom message on the login screen before
 users log in, with optional auto-clear after the next login.
 .
 Features include a live countdown display, system tray support,
 9 languages, and persistent settings.
